      "span_text": "Remark5: To demonstrate various cases we consider two scenarios with inputs for In addition, a network designer may stipulate that some sub-networks may not be further divisible if they do not satisfy at least one of the following threshold conditions: a) Their combined \"weight\" {incoming and outgoing flow w} is lower than a specified threshold; b) The number of users in the cluster {sub-network} is smaller than a specified by the designer threshold."
